description.en:
What is the project about?
Babydogeceo, TwitterWallet is our main utility. Where you can send and receive crypto using Twitter. After signing up and depositing crypto into your account.  BabyDogeCEO x ELONMUSK develops twitter payment ($TwitterWallet) to replace Apple Pay - PAYPAL leads the Crypto trend in the world. You can able to send the money using the twitter @id  like  "@WalletCEO  @ElonMusk" and it will transfer your crypto currency from your account to the recipient's account (in this case #ElonMusk). you can tweet something like "@WalletCEO send 1 BNB to @ElonMusk" and it will transfer 1 BNB from your account to the recipient's account (in this case #ElonMusk). We are currently focused on BSC because of its high speed and low fees. The average wait time for a transaction is 4 seconds. We build it in EVM chain, So you can able to  use this wallet anywhere like  trust wallet and metamask by inserting your seed phrase .  Holders can  emphasize to 7% reward Holders there's no need to  staking and all . they will get their rewards automatically from every  buy and sell.

What makes your project unique?
- KYC-AUDIT - Renounced OwnerShip, New technology transmitted from ELONMUSK, CEX PRE-LISTED VINDAX, 7% tax reward holder
TwitterWallet, Mintnfts, Staking, swap...Supported by social media influencers & 500+ KOLS, No Token & No Unlock Development Team, Big Marketing Wallet, Renounced ownership, DIDBTOK, AMABinance, Super Burn token. Renounced ownership: https://bscscan.com/tx/0x43df751b7b89aafb07c53e5bc2052d1022a3b25e9363d115e306db06b409094f

History of your project.


What’s next for your project?
Used 30000$ for pre-launch marketing (CEX PRE-LISTED VINDAX - BTOK - Binance...) - After launch #BaByDogeCEO will continue the chain of stronger marketing activities: CG China & CMC China. Trending dextools, avex after 4-10 days of launching, complete the social

What can your token be used for?
TwitterWallet, Mintnfts, Staking, Swap
